{"id":"chenaanah","term":"Chenaanah","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Merchant. (1.) A Benjamite (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 7:10\">1 Chr. 7:10</a>). (2.) The father of Zedekiah (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Kings 22:11\">1 Kings 22:11</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Kings 22:24\">24</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["1 Chronicles 7:10","1 Kings 22:11","1 Kings 22:24"]}